{"tid":2410402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭預告 有望6月出獄再見大家","createTime":"2021-02-16T14:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:43:47.000Z","uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2535e4f876e312f77707aa52dbbf1e9db0938ce6","tid":2410402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aFR97f0ICt0T55KNodB9IIl8P2w=/468x263/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNFCDQ2FH5HCFMCMCODDGJA2EE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaFR97f0ICt0T55KNodB9IIl8P2w%3D%2F468x263%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNFCDQ2FH5HCFMCMCODDGJA2EE.jpg&h=e37e4402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然疫情之下，今個農曆年冇乜地方好去，但係比起身在獄中嘅抗爭者，大家總算有多啲啲嘅自由。因為去年6.21包圍警總案被判監嘅前香港眾志成員周庭，喺獄中只能靠睇書、聽收音機、睇信嚟解悶。好彩今日終於傳嚟好消息，就係周庭有望6月出返嚟。"},{"pid":"da9c06f397c17770fe97a6ecc1f3898c7f4efb98","tid":2410402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"社交網站專頁admin今日出post話，新年期間有朋友探過周庭兼同佢拜年，周庭講起近排嘅生活，就係啱啱睇完《挪威的森林》，遲啲就打算再睇村上春樹同埋東野圭吾嘅書。<br />\n<br />\n講到獄中生活時，周庭答謝大家關心之餘話：「坐監期間，精神和身體狀況都吃不消。希望6月出冊後可以暫時休息，休養身體。希望可以有休息空間。」言語間透露咗佢有機會喺6月出返嚟。話就話6月距離而家只有4個月，但係獄中嘅日子並唔易過，尤其是周庭喺今年初先至被送去用嚟監禁甲級犯嘅大欖女懲教所，只能夠寄望佢可以頂住呀。"},{"pid":"83159137c94a7f946f05a925b1a05343fa3debd2","tid":2410402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"係咪有人貼左 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb5e172e8374c6ce477e5b724a85626ebb2bdf96","tid":2410402,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGlz5v_nQhH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGlz5v_nQhH&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=543ab09f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGlz5v_nQhH&h=637f92ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CGlz5v_nQhH</a><br />\n<br />\n發覺有個攝影師專同佢影相 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}